63  RTPS_DllAPI inline const StructMemberFlag& member_flags() const { return m_member_flags; }
64  RTPS_DllAPI inline StructMemberFlag& member_flags() { return m_member_flags; }
65

67  RTPS_DllAPI inline void member_type_id(TypeIdentifier &&_member_type_id) { m_member_type_id = std::move(_member_type_id); }

73  RTPS_DllAPI void serialize(eprosima::fastcdr::Cdr &cdr) const;
